                            <li><strong>Category</strong>: Desktop Application</li>
                            <li><strong>Purpose</strong>: Software Development 2    </li>
                            <li><strong>Project date</strong>: August, 2021 - November, 2021</li>
                            <li><strong>Project URL</strong>: <a href="https://github.com/lestify12/Elementum">Elementum</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="portfolio-description">
                        <h2>
                            Vaccination Card Windows Form app using C#
                        </h2>
                        <p>
                            The Vaccination Card App is a software application that enables people to digitally save and retrieve their COVID-19 vaccination data. To use the app, individuals typically need to enter their personal data, such as their name, birth date, and contact information, in addition to information about their vaccination, such as the vaccine type, date of administration, and vaccination site. The app is intended to be a secure and user-friendly tool for individuals to monitor their vaccination status and share their vaccination data with healthcare providers or employers. Additionally, the app can set reminders for individuals to schedule their second vaccine dose and track any possible side effects.
                        </p>
                    </div>
